<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-829] Mirror maker needs to share the migration tool request channel </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-829</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;0.8 mirror maker suffers from the same drawbacks that the original version of the migration tool did. The consumer gets blocked if its producer queue is full, even if there are other idle producers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12639224">KAFKA-829</key>
